WISHLISTADD_DESCRIPTION: Use this command to add a character to your personal wishlist. This action has no direct benefit or advantage associated with it
ADD_CHARACTERS_ERROR: {{author}} You cannot add more characters to your wishlist
INCREASE_CAPACITY: Unlock more slots by using the `{{prefix}}wl` command and clicking on the {{emoji}} icon
NO_CHARACTER_FOUND: {{author}} Could not find that character. Use the command `{{prefix}}wa -f <Name>` for an exact search
VERSION_ALREADY_EXISTS: {{author}} You already have **{{name}}** in your wishlist for version `{{version}}`
VERSION_ADDED: {{author}} Successfully added **{{name}}** to your wishlist for version `{{version}}`
